title: JCC Soccer Teams Defeat Corning
text:
JCC Soccer Teams Defeat Corning   13, 2015 at 7:57 AM   13, 2015 at 8:04 AM EDT 
Men's and women's soccer teams at Jefferson Community College both had a good day Monday against Corning Community College. The men won big over their competition with a final score of 9-2 and the Lady Cannoneers squeaked past Corning with a score of 2-1. Watch the video for highlights.
